tournament.motion:
This house, as the environmental movement, would adopt ecocentrism over anthropocentrism.

Ecocentrism refers to the narrative that the earth must be taken care of regardless of its perceived value. Anthropocentrism refers to the narrative that the earth must be taken care of for future generations to come.
This house regrets the trend of successful sportspeople prolonging their competitive careers beyond the usual age of retirement (e.g. Lebron James, Tom Brady, Cristiano Ronaldo)

THW actively prioritize Universal Basic Income over Universal Basic Services

Universal Basic Services (UBS) is a system that guarantees free or affordable access to essential public services, such as healthcare, education, housing, and transportation, aiming to meet basic human needs and promote social equity whereas a Universal Basic Income (UBI) is an unconditional cash payment given monthly to all citizens or residents, regardless of their employment status, to ensure a basic standard of living and reduce poverty. For the purposes of this debate, the amount given to a citizen monthly under a UBI program is proportional to the amount the government would have spent to subsidise the citizen across the various UBS programs.

TH as a socially conscious, up and coming lawyer would choose to follow a career as a prosecutor rather than a defense lawyer.

Prosecutors represent the government in criminal cases. Their primary responsibility is to present evidence and legal arguments in an effort to prove that the accused individual is guilty of the charges brought against them. Defense attorneys, on the other hand, represent individuals who have been accused of crimes. Their role is to protect the legal rights of their clients by challenging the prosecution's case and presenting evidence or arguments to demonstrate their client's innocence or to seek a fair and just outcome.

This house believes that it is in the interest of the NPP Government to create a DOGE for the Sri Lankan State

A Department of Government Efficiency is a government body tasked with streamlining public sector operations to reduce costs, eliminate redundancies, and improve service delivery. This often includes undertaking structural reforms such as downsizing the public workforce, consolidating departments, and automating administrative functions.
This house regrets the market dominancce of queer romance fiction created for and by non-queer audiences.

THP a world in which Lucifer did not bring knowledge to humans at the cost of exiting the Garden of Eden.

In Christian tradition, Lucifer is a fallen angel who rebelled against God and later is associated with the serpent in Eden who tempted Adam and Eve to eat from the Tree of Knowledge. This act gave humanity knowledge but led to their expulsion from the Garden.
